; Source: Computer Science Logo Style, Volume 1, Chapter 10 turtle-geometry examples.
; This fixture is a compact deterministic drawing modeled on the chapter's
; square/polygon walk patterns so the conformance suite can assert turtle state
; and headless drawing events without a window.
clearscreen
setpc 14
setpensize 2
repeat 4 [forward 50 right 90]
penup
right 45
forward 10
pendown
setlabelheight 9
label "done
fill
